title: S15 Ep77: Supernatural News/ParaShare:  High Spirits Edition
itunes:title: Supernatural News/ParaShare:  High Spirits Edition
description:
Darkness Radio Returns with Supernatural News/ParaShare High Spirits Edition!
Listen Here Anytime:

Dave & Tim bring you all the News worth hearing this week with a deep dive into the bizarre & Supernatural. From Witches to Ghosts, Strange Creatures to Unusual Funerals, stories that will help you escape the worries of the world and surround you with it's wonder from around the world. All that PLUS your real life encounters featured in our ParaShare segment.

To see the stories Dave & Tim discuss on air, visit www.DarknessRadio.com and click the NEWS tab.Darkness Radiodarknessradio.com
